1...Qg4 2.Re4
{ Permanently laying claim to the e-file. Now Black has no active plan and
he can only sit back and passively wait, hoping that White won't be able to
figure out a way to break through. In the position after 1. Bc6, both sides are playing for two possible results: Black will either lose or draw, and
White will either win or draw. Obviously, nobody would want to be in Black's shoes. }
