{ since 19. fxg3?? Rxd1 wins a whole piece. } ) ( { After } 18.Bd3
{ play might have continued } 18...Nfd5 19.Ne4 Bf4
{ and White has absolutely nothing. 19.c4 Nb4 is annoying since it's
impossible for the d3 -Bishop to defend itself while also keeping an eye on
both c4 and a2. } ) *

