{ Level: 2200 on up. } 26...e4 $1
{ [%mdl 32768] Suddenly the Bishop isn't a Tall-Pawn anymore! Turning the dormant Bishop into a serious force is well worth the sacrificed pawn. This kind of thing, and the psychological processes involved in actually playing such a move, will be explored in Part Four, Psychological Meanderings. }
27.Nxe4 Bd4+ 28.Kh1 a4
{ Black has been very methodical: first he activates his Bishop, then he
forces White's King to step to the far right of the board (away from the
real fight on the queenside!), and finally he begins his assault against White's queenside pawns. }
