} 18.Nc7 $5
{ A surprise, but it fits in nicely with our overview of Bishops. Carlsen
realizes that the enemy Bishop, though ugly, is actually a good defensive
piece (in other words, it's inactive but useful). Due to this, he exchanges the Bishop for the Knight, which will force the King to defend f5. }
18...Rag8 19.Nxe6 Kxe6 20.Rxg8 Nxg8
