Rcc3 ( { More natural is } 45...Rxa5 { , but then } 46.Rh8+ Kf7 47.Rxg5 $1
{ leads to a Rook endgame where White enjoys a three pawn advantage. } )
46.Rf6+ Kg8 47.Ra7 Rc2 48.Rd6
