{ had to be tried. } ) 6.Nxg6+ Kd6 7.Rf8 Kd5 8.Nxf4+ Kd4 9.Nxh5 Kc3 10.Kg3
Rc4 11.Nxg7 a4 12.h5 a3 13.h6 a2 14.Ra8 { No dignity for poor Portela. }
1-0

[Event "How to Reassess Your Chess "]
[Site "?"]
