Ultimately it came down to having faith in the power of 'lesser' imbalances
over material. And this is a concept that you can (slowly but surely) train into your psyche at almost any rating level. 

REMEMBER If you create 'imbalance vision' and make the search for (and
understanding of) imbalances an addiction, your playing strength will take a quantum leap forward. }
