and try hard to make it work! } 1.Nf3 { [%mdl 32768] } d5 2.d4 Nf6 3.c4 c6
4.Nc3 dxc4 5.a4 Bf5 6.Ne5 e6 7.f3 Bb4 8.e4 Bxe4 9.fxe4 Nxe4 10.Bd2 Qxd4
