defense of c7. } 5...b6 ( { • } 5...Nb4 6.d4 Nxd5 7.dxe5 Qb4+ 8.Bd2 Qxb2
9.cxd5 Bb4 10.Rc1
{ and White's advantage is obvious-huge center, space, lead in development,
