Nxg3 ( { Another bloody example is } 11...Bxd4 12.Qxh5+ Kf8 13.Bd5 Qd7
14.Bh6+ Bg7 15.Rae1 Ne5 16.f4 { and Black can quietly give up. } ) 12.Nxc6
bxc6 13.Bxc6+ Bd7 14.Re1+ Kf8 15.Qd5
