16.Bxf8 dxc3 17.b3 Qd2+ 18.Qxd2 cxd2+ 19.Kxd2 Kxf8 20.gxf5 Rd8+ 21.Ke2 Bxa1
22.Rxa1 gxf5 { and Black is a pawn up in the endgame. } ) 14.Qd4 $2
