{ This crushing move was probably played instantly (I'm sure he already
considered the game to be over), which explains why a magnificent player
like Ivkov missed } 19.cxd6 cxd6 20.Nxd6 $1 Qxd6 21.Bc5 Qb8 22.Bxe7 )
19...Ne8 20.Rxf8+ Kxf8 21.Qa3 Kf7 22.c6 bxc6 23.bxc6 Bc8 24.Nb5 $1
{ Black could have resigned here, but he decided to sit back and watch his
esteemed foe cut him up a bit more. } 24...Kf8 25.Qa5 h6 26.Ba7 Qa8 27.Nxc7
Nxc7 28.Qxc7 Ba6 29.Nb6 1-0

