41.Bb3 Bf6 42.f4 Ng6 43.f5 Ngf8 44.h4 Kh7 45.Kh3 Kg7 46.g4 Kh7 47.Bc1 Bg7
48.g5 hxg5 49.hxg5 Kh8 { And Black resigned without waiting for the reply. }
1-0

