1.c4 { [%mdl 32768] } c5 2.Nf3 g6 3.d4 cxd4 4.Nxd4 Nc6 5.e4
{ Transposing back into a Maroczy Bind. } 5...Bg7 6.Be3 Nf6 7.Nc3 b6 8.Nc2
{ Following the old adage that the side with more space should avoid
unnecessary exchanges. } 8...Bb7 9.Be2 O-O 10.Qd2 d6 11.O-O Qd7 12.f3 Rfd8
