30.Qxd4 Qe5 31.Qd7 Rc7 ( 31...Qc5+ $1 32.Kh1 Qf2 33.Qe6+ Kg7 34.Qd7+ Kh8
{ gives Black a clear advantage. } ) 32.Qd8+ Kg7 33.Bg5 Rf7 34.h4 h6 35.Bd2
Qc5+ 36.Kh2 Qe7 ( 36...Bxf3 $1 { was the way to go. } ) 37.Qxe7 Rxe7 38.h5
