is fine. } 40.Nc5 { 40.Kh1 Nd7 41.Qg3 Nf8 } 40...Bxc5 41.dxc5
{ 41.Rxc5 Nd7 42.R5c3 Nf8 with ...Ne6 to follow doesn't worry Black. }
41...Qa7 42.Bd4 Nd7 43.Kh1 Nf8 44.Rg3 Rg7 45.Rcg1 Re8 $1 46.Qf3
{ 46.e6 Rxe6 47.Bxg7 Kxg7 can only favor Black. } 46...Re6
{ is nothing for White. 

In the actual game, White got outplayed. } ) 38...Bxc5 39.Rxc5 Qxb3 40.Rxa5
