{ The prized e6-pawn sacrifices itself, knowing that it will immediately be
reincarnated via e5-e6. The point of the sacrifice is that it allows
White's dark-squared Bishop to enter the battle, it leads to the black King being forced away from the embattled area, and it also forces Black's
dark-squared Bishop to the vulnerable e7-square. } 24...Bxe7 25.e6+ Kb7
26.Nf5
